# E-Commerce Product Store вҖ” Implementation Plan

## 1. Tech Stack

| Layer | Choice | Rationale |
|-------|--------|-----------|
| Framework | Next.js 16 (App Router) | SSR, SEO, file-based routing, API routes |
| Language | TypeScript 5 (strict) | Type safety, strict mode |
| UI Library | Ant Design 6 | Production-grade, built-in RTL + dark mode support |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v4 | Utility-first, RTL variants (`rtl:`, `ltr:`) |
| Server State | @tanstack/react-query v5 | Caching, dedup, infinite scroll |
| Client State | Redux Toolkit | Auth session + theme preference |
| Auth | JWT in httpOnly cookies | XSS-safe, CSRF mitigated via SameSite |
| i18n | next-intl | Cookie-based locale (not URL prefix), RTL support |
| Theme | Ant Design theme tokens + Tailwind `dark:` | System toggle + persist in cookie |
| Infinite Scroll | IntersectionObserver + useInfiniteQuery | Standard performant pattern |
| HTTP Client | Axios with interceptors | Auto cookie forwarding |
| API | FakeStoreAPI + custom Next.js API routes | Auth via our own API, products via FakeStoreAPI |
| **Tooling** | | |
| Formatter | Prettier 3 + prettier-plugin-tailwindcss | Consistent style |
| Linter | ESLint 9 (flat config) + next/core-web-vitals | Catch bugs early |
| Hooks | Husky 9 + lint-staged | Pre-commit quality gate |
| Editor | EditorConfig | Cross-IDE consistency |

