## 3. Dark/Light Mode Architecture

```
User toggles theme
        в”Ӯ
        в–ј
Client: set cookie `theme=dark|light` + update Redux
        в”Ӯ
        в–ј
Ant Design ConfigProvider: `theme.algorithm = theme.darkAlgorithm | theme.defaultAlgorithm`
        в”Ӯ
        в–ј
Tailwind: `dark:` variants via `class` strategy (Ant Design adds `dark` class to `<html>`)
```

### How they coexist:

| Concern | Mechanism |
|---------|-----------|
| Locale + direction | `next-intl` reads cookie вҶ’ Redux `locale` вҶ’ AntD `direction` |
| Theme | Cookie вҶ’ Redux `theme` вҶ’ AntD `algorithm` + Tailwind `dark:` |
| Persistence | Both locale and theme stored in cookies (server-readable) |
| Hydration | Cookie read in middleware, passed to layout to prevent flash |

