## 4. Direction-Aware Styling Strategy

### Ant Design components
Ant Design handles RTL internally via `ConfigProvider direction="rtl"`. No extra work.

### Custom Tailwind styles
Use Tailwind's RTL variants for layout:

```tsx
<div className="flex gap-2 rtl:space-x-reverse">
  <span className="ml-2 rtl:mr-2 rtl:ml-0">Text</span>
</div>
```

Or CSS logical properties (preferred for new code):
```css
margin-inline-start: 0.5rem;
padding-inline-end: 1rem;
```

### Grid & flex
Ant Design's Row/Col and Flex components auto-flip in RTL. Tailwind grid remains symmetric (no change needed unless explicit left/right).

