## 8. Route Design

| Route | Type | Auth | Locale-aware | Description |
|-------|------|------|-------------|-------------|
| `/` | Page | No | Yes | Product list with filters, infinite scroll |
| `/product/[id]` | Page (SSR) | No | Yes | Product details with dynamic metadata |
| `/login` | Page | No | Yes | Login form |
| `/register` | Page | No | Yes | Registration form |
| `/api/auth/register` | POST | No | No | Create user, set JWT cookie |
| `/api/auth/login` | POST | No | No | Verify credentials, set JWT cookie |
| `/api/auth/me` | GET | Yes | No | Return current user from cookie |

**No `[locale]` segment in URL.** Locale from cookie only.

